 The major characteristics of the image-matching algorithm for DOGS-AP are as follows [7]–[9]
:

1)area-based grid matching with cross-correlations;
2)simultaneous triplet image matching on epipolar geometry;
3)coarse-to-fine (CTF) image pyramid;
4)cross-correlation patch size dynamic optimization.

